like":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T19:09:10.000Z","msg":"好好睇,我好鐘意<br />\n世界觀好完整,每一樣野都有原因<br />\n劇情好好,人類同化鼠個矛盾位做得到出嚟,雖然人類好仆街,但係咁樣已經係最好嘅結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n動畫漫畫都有睇,原作小說都買埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有,依句真係好正,一句話總括咗成個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYM8Ejc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYM8Ejc.jpg&h=87dcec05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想像力能改變一切"},{"pid":"50b75f8805f97fed12c2e3c1eb9a5163874c2008","tid":2377183,"uid":54930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T08:45:52.000Z","msg":"btw有樣野唔屌唔得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9839517488d13d36876ed9080dfcc6abee6df2","tid":2377183,"uid":68569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10edea4b24b53ccba045db347cc0986e341f8df9","tid":2377183,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"分開左幾次去睇,每次睇幾集,岩岩終於睇完,<br />\n雖然唔鐘意個故事,節奏又怕,大部份時間又唔知個故事想講乜<br />\n但睇完同意係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"多謝推薦 一晚睇曬七本漫畫"},{"pid":"185312bd6fca82de9b4a206b539d115e9c531d44","tid":2377183,"uid":326135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"睇過小說<br />\n<br />\n一直覺得史奎拉死得幾慘<br />\n<br />\n只不過係冇能力嘅舊人類<br />\n就要俾新人類扭曲、勞役、屠殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n史奎拉只係想攞返屬於佢哋原本人類應有嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但話晒主視角先係我哋熟知嘅「人類」<br />\n而史奎拉係化鼠，不斷利用主角群<br />\n直至結尾之前難免有種非我莫屬、死有餘辜嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n然後無啦啦話化鼠係人類<br />\n嗰陣睇真係好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw奇狼丸都型<br />\n兩隻化鼠都係我最鍾意嘅角色"},{"pid":"2b91